<ol>
<li><strong>Refreshed content drives 106% to 260% more organic traffic</strong> than untouched posts, measured across HubSpot and Backlinko case studies.</li>
<li><strong>82% of high-ranking posts start losing traffic within 12 to 24 months</strong> without maintenance, according to Semrush content audit data.</li>
