<li><strong>Businesses that update content quarterly see 42% better results</strong> than those that refresh annually, per Moz 2025 analysis.</li>
<li><strong>Adding 40 to 44 internal links during updates produces 4× more Google clicks</strong> than pages with 0 to 4 links, per Zyppy SEO analysis of 23 million links.</li>
</ol>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>The Content Compound Effect:</strong> Consistent content updates compound your SEO investment. We publish and refresh 30 optimized articles monthly so your content archive keeps working.
<a href="/pricing/">Start for $1 →</a></p>
